x,k \ge 0
2x + k = 4
2\cdot5^m = 2^x + 2^{x + k} = 2^x(1 + 2^k)
5^m = 2^{x - 1}(1 + 2^k)
x - 1 > 0
5^m
x - 1 = 0 \implies x = 1 \implies k = 4 - 2 = 2
